'''角赤旋螺'''（学名：''{{lang|la|Pleuroploca trapezium}}''）是一個[[海螺|海螺]]的[[物种|物种]]，屬於[[新腹足目|新腹足目]][[细带螺科|细带螺科]]的[[海洋生物|海洋]][[腹足纲|腹足纲]][[软体动物|软体动物]]{{r|WoRMS_217071}}。舊屬[[前鰓類|前鰓類]][[旋螺科|旋螺科]]{{r|正中|page1=596 |shell_1137}}，日常生活提及的「旋螺」常指本物種{{r|正中|page1=596}}。本物種一般作為食用而被捕獲，但當其[[水管溝|水管溝]]被鋸走後，亦有用作[[螺號|螺號]]使用<ref>[http://www.sealifebase.org/summary/SpeciesSummary.php?id=87018 Sealifebase : Pleuroploca trapezium]; accessed : 24 November 2010</ref><ref>[https://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&q=cache:DFKwYspW_5sJ:www.asianfisheriessociety.org/modules/wfdownloads/visit.php%3Fcid%3D21%26lid%3D644+%22Pleuroploca+trapezium%22&hl=en&gl=be&pid=bl&srcid=ADGEEShV4UCHopMOS3sIQWKTZ3lrP0DjUhn2eglt0JSBmq2QOrA1AOtXCtbnixlAHLL-NEFDSJfYdvnr1DVOeebBenKpmvf6TbuxdMlOQOWJ_v1lc3leXdwtjHDg8m_m8MHHHw0_Vwbt&sig=AHIEtbQq-98_GB-z_axPIRYZCWPI1Vm-sg Felicia Shanthini and Jamila Patterson, Processing of horse conch, Pleuroploca trapezium, (Fasciolariidae) meat into meat balls; Asian Fisheries Science 18 (2005): 265-273] {{Wayback|url=https://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&q=cache%3ADFKwYspW_5sJ%3Awww.asianfisheriessociety.org%2Fmodules%2Fwfdownloads%2Fvisit.php%3Fcid%3D21%26lid%3D644+%22Pleuroploca+trapezium%22&hl=en&gl=be&pid=bl&srcid=ADGEEShV4UCHopMOS3sIQWKTZ3lrP0DjUhn2eglt0JSBmq2QOrA1AOtXCtbnixlAHLL-NEFDSJfYdvnr1DVOeebBenKpmvf6TbuxdMlOQOWJ_v1lc3leXdwtjHDg8m_m8MHHHw0_Vwbt&sig=AHIEtbQq-98_GB-z_axPIRYZCWPI1Vm-sg |date=20170517013818 }}.</ref>。

